d？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正嘅Endgame，只會係政權被摧毀之日，或者香港人被摧毀之時</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁用Endgame號召人出黎有咩問題？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n常言道心態決定境界，錯誤既Endgame心態，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">隨時會令香港人墮入萬劫不復嘅境地</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果聽日就係世界末日，你會做D咩？<br />\n相信大部分人都會選擇做D<strong>「豁出去」</strong>嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Endgame心態，好可能會令某D手足係呢個時候就「豁出去」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>「最後一次喎，我死都唔撤架喇。」</em></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果香港人已經進化到全民皆兵，咁嘅心態或者可以加速整個運動進程<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但現實係香港人未進化到咁</strong>，死都唔撤嘅結果會係點大家可想而知<br />\n<br />\n每多一個手足有咁嘅心態同行動，<strong>好可能我地就會損失多一員</strong><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得七一梁繼平話過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地一輸就係十年，公民社會會一沉百踩</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n輸，就係再冇人出黎，會出黎嘅都已經係監倉渡過緊十年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>「我就唔信佢拉得曬，外面咁多手足會撐住」</em></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但現實往往係殘酷，可能有手足就算保釋緊都仲會出去，但亦都有好多手足會因為恐懼或者絕望而唔再出去<br />\n<br />\n每次有手足被捕，唔單止係失去左被捕嘅果位手足，<strong>更加係增加緊其他手足嘅恐懼同絕望</strong>，損失嘅可能唔止係一個手足<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">再咁落去，此消彼長之下，其實要輸，真係唔遠</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>「咁係咪以後唔洗出去，個個唔出咪唔會俾人拉」</em></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔係，只係出去嘅時候要有正確嘅心態</strong><br />\n<br />\n隨住國際介入嘅力度越黎越強，中共嘅打壓都唔會一時三刻停低，更好可能加強打壓<br />\n<br />\n下下吹Endgame，咁到出23條、公安執法、戒嚴令、解放軍、坦克入城果時點算？<br />\n<br />\n唔應該係：今次係最後一次，今次唔出下次冇得你出<br />\n<br />\n<strong>應該係：今次一定要出，今次出黎係為左下一次仲有得出，直到政權倒下</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每一場抗爭唔單止要爭取我地當日想要嘅效果，亦都係為下一場抗爭作鋪墊，直到勝利為止</span></span></strong> </strong><br />\n<br />\n有咁嘅心態，你先會有動力強化自己，先會有動力照顧好自己，照顧好身邊嘅手足，一齊繼續走落去 <br />\n<br />\n除左不斷增強自己嘅戰力同智謀，希望大家都可以時刻調整好自己嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終有一日我地會係煲底慶祝勝利來臨</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">多謝你睇到哩度，希望你可以幫手推POST，分享畀更多手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">今日亦都唔係Endgame，你唔需要去裸跑</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcc0a53f3131bb65b0d3964f261b1c712190789","tid":2040333,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ded9904011286a141b0f9b8cfd54897dd92578b","tid":2040333,"uid":72344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"幫你推 高質po"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7693c1e6e7fc6001876b7ce0844ac1e4842cc47","tid":2040333,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"明明而家先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210dab752ac312e8a901585cb6d6591322433950","tid":2040333,"uid":17503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"今次出黎係為左下一次仲有得出，直到政權倒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1a367a89921c8b25305e971ea2eb146413e089","tid":2040333,"uid":176460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"748f64366149f19c5de6e3fbf4e0ebacb4feb357","tid":2040333,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"推意志post!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386666befdd79f796b309c661b48d937a2909c6a","tid":2040333,"uid":273627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得end game心態唔係最大問題<br />\n<br />\n反而係目標唔清晰/冇共識<br />\n<br />\n然後加上end game心態，就會想搏一搏，唔理乜撚都做啲嘢先<br />\n<br />\n最後容易變咗emotion driven而唔係purpose driven<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好文，subscribed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851d381b202bce3dbff5b1a230f5b8cc3f503b20","tid":2040333,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:44:17.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"89b4cf4a0224224013cdc94f188672c5013c6ca0","tid":2040333,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d68c213c6e0812041a60ebe2cb7772eb8bb629b4","tid":2040333,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6709eeadda98713c928467cb29baca9eafab3863","tid":2040333,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> （由於上一個post沉得太快，而家改過個topic重新開過） </span><br />\n<br />\n524 同 527 傷亡有幾慘重唔需要多講，檢討嘅目的係要下次做得更好<br />\n<br />\n而除左戰略同戰術之外，<strong>心態都係一個好重要嘅因素</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次想講嘅係</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「Endgame心態」</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXG59tS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXG59tS.gif&h=adfb7589&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國歌法同國安法來得突然，相信好多手足係早幾日都有強烈嘅<strong>亡國感</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢種亡國感驅使我地係524同527再次走上街頭向世界掙扎<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「Endgame」</strong>、<strong>「最後一次」</strong>，就係其中一個好多人用黎號召524同527嘅講法<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><em>「國歌法過左，第日出黎播首國歌就可以拉曬你地」<br />\n「國安法過埋，你呼吸都可以砌死你」<br />\n「今次唔出，第日就冇機會出」</em><br />\n...</blockquote></div><br />\n的而且確，兩條惡法係急速加劇左中共對香港人嘅打壓，香港嘅自由將會高速消失<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但距離所謂嘅 Endgame，係咪真係咁近？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n527啱啱過去，場Game end左未？<br />\n<br />\n如果國歌法二讀已經係香港人嘅Endgame，咁528嘅國安法表決又算係咩？<br />\n<br />\n國安法過左之後，香港人係咪就唔會再抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n我唔相信香港人會就此停步，亦唔相信中共嘅打壓會止於國安法<br />\n<br />\n<strong>既然兩邊嘅玩家都唔會就此停步，場Game又點會咁快End？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正嘅Endgame，只會係政權被摧毀之日，或者香港人被摧毀之時</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁用Endgame號召人出黎有咩問題？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n常言道心態決定境界，錯誤既Endgame心態，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">隨時會令香港人墮入萬劫不復嘅境地</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果聽日就係世界末日，你會做D咩？<br />\n相信大部分人都會選擇做D<strong>「豁出去」</strong>嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Endgame心態，好可能會令某D手足係呢個時候就「豁出去」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>「最後一次喎，我死都唔撤架喇。」</em></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果香港人已經進化到全民皆兵，咁嘅心態或者可以加速整個運動進程<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但現實係香港人未進化到咁</strong>，死都唔撤嘅結果會係點大家可想而知<br />\n<br />\n每多一個手足有咁嘅心態同行動，<strong>好可能我地就會損失多一員</strong><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得七一梁繼平話過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地一輸就係十年，公民社會會一沉百踩</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n輸，就係再冇人出黎，會出黎嘅都已經係監倉渡過緊十年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>「我就唔信佢拉得曬，外面咁多手足會撐住」</em></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但現實往往係殘酷，可能有手足就算保釋緊都仲會出去，但亦都有好多手足會因為恐懼或者絕望而唔再出去<br />\n<br />\n每次有手足被捕，唔單止係失去左被捕嘅果位手足，<strong>更加係增加緊其他手足嘅恐懼同絕望</strong>，損失嘅可能唔止係一個手足<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">再咁落去，此消彼長之下，其實要輸，真係唔遠</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>「咁係咪以後唔洗出去，個個唔出咪唔會俾人拉」</em></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔係，只係出去嘅時候要有正確嘅心態</strong><br />\n<br />\n隨住國際介入嘅力度越黎越強，中共嘅打壓都唔會一時三刻停低，更好可能加強打壓<br />\n<br />\n下下吹Endgame，咁到出23條、公安執法、戒嚴令、解放軍、坦克入城果時點算？<br />\n<br />\n唔應該係：今次係最後一次，今次唔出下次冇得你出<br />\n<br />\n<strong>應該係：今次一定要出，今次出黎係為左下一次仲有得出，直到政權倒下</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每一場抗爭唔單止要爭取我地當日想要嘅效果，亦都係為下一場抗爭作鋪墊，直到勝利為止</span></span></strong> </strong><br />\n<br />\n有咁嘅心態，你先會有動力強化自己，先會有動力照顧好自己，照顧好身邊嘅手足，一齊繼續走落去 <br />\n<br />\n除左不斷增強自己嘅戰力同智謀，希望大家都可以時刻調整好自己嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終有一日我地會係煲底慶祝勝利來臨</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">多謝你睇到哩度，希望你可以幫手推POST，分享畀更多手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">今日亦都唔係Endgame，你唔需要去裸跑</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4a31b2ba59eadd6a9ec8bbbf6fc3eb362c9f1b","tid":2040333,"uid":13118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"放棄就真係一切都完結"},{"pid":"482b150f9402bf0cf90793c97848861c1d0136e2","tid":2040333,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7693c1e6e7fc6001876b7ce0844ac1e4842cc47","tid":2040333,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"明明而家先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff956127d47ad06a91ea2fc43364a09ff40ac19f","tid":2040333,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210dab752ac312e8a901585cb6d6591322433950","tid":2040333,"uid":17503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"今次出黎係為左下一次仲有得出，直到政權倒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:46:49.000Z","msg":"終有一日我地會係煲底慶祝勝利來臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/no